        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 10. Records of Northern Hemisphere species of Jassa that were found in the eastern and/or western North Pacific and seas. Red dot: identification confirmed by specimen examination; green triangle: literature record (Supplementary Table S1) with identification not confirmed but judged likely to be this species; blue x: suspected or known to be on the hull or interior of a boat or ship." ;
